RH-MergeRequest: 251: qemu-img: Fix exit code for errors closing the image
RH-Bugzilla: 2147617
RH-Acked-by: Hanna Czenczek <hreitz@redhat.com>
RH-Acked-by: Stefan Hajnoczi <stefanha@redhat.com>
